{"tid":1418090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術］其實要搞擺工、搞經濟唔一定要不合作/去整road block","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:07:02.000Z","uid":63118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6d974956f768f4723c971e30562f1402b42a7820","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"之前有個巴打咪教去剪交通燈電源<br />\n<br />\n我突然聯想到 想請教大定係咪如果某啲地區交通燈咪會堵塞哂果區交通 再塞埋主要道路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為啲車唔知幾時行得 會塞死哂<br />\n政府又要花時間去整返好啲燈<br />\n<br />\n港鐵人流多 門又關唔埋又開唔到車 啲人返唔到工 <br />\n變相擺工 最後影響埋經濟？<br />\n<br />\n我唔支持大家做法犯野 千萬不要去試 <br />\n只係想同大家討論下有咩情況下會影響到香港經濟<br />\n<br />\n表明立場： 不支持任何犯法、影響社會活動"},{"pid":"588b8abbac2b8ebcbadda87929cbf3e33471c565","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:50:04.000Z","msg":"搵唔返個教巴打整街燈個post俾大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e28b680d0b03b03833410cad4fc1b861ba7c4d2","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:52:59.000Z","msg":"罷工的後續，經濟戰！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1408245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1408245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另外呢個經濟戰嘅方法又有冇效都可以加埋入黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b255832d97f921831f945bd621bcb2ae3468f03f","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:17.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台"},{"pid":"8f2d95c85731cf327f19ed675108d96f4863a8c8","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:47.000Z","msg":"經濟學術討論post"},{"pid":"cd68c2162b1aa4a42fccd21ae6261c4f42989607","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8294ce672ad63fab88b0f4c3868f59122e5a74a4","tid":1418090,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,